                                <h4 class="section-subheading">There is always a reason to buy your buddy a nice cold beer. <br>Beer Me is a Web & Mobile app that allows you to send your friends drinks from anywhere, even if you're not with them.</h4>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </section>
